---
title: Baked Chicken Parmigiana with Crispy Potatoes and Blistered Green Beans
description: Revel in all your favourite flavours of the classic Chicken Parmesan, but with a twist! This easy baked chicken breast topped with fresh tomato and melted mozzarella will have you wondering why it took you this long to recreate your favourite pub meal.
